  <entry>
    <title>Late night thinking</title>
    <link href="/2024/10/17/%E5%A4%9C%E6%9C%89%E6%89%80%E6%83%B3/"/>
    <url>/2024/10/17/%E5%A4%9C%E6%9C%89%E6%89%80%E6%83%B3/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Charming and fascinating rain fell from the firmament, rippling around aquarius. Clamorous world seems like a whole world away in a deep trance. Ethereal cloud and mist embraced me in the stillness. Melancholy soul discharged from the body, leading me into the dream of the butterfly lovers at a slow pace.</p><h2 id="夜有所想"><a href="#夜有所想" class="headerlink" title="夜有所想"></a>夜有所想</h2><p>醉雨落涟漪<br>喧闹恍隔世<br>飘渺云雾间<br>魂断梦梁柱</p><p>令人陶醉的雨从天空落下，在水中荡起了涟漪，喧闹的尘世恍惚间仿佛隔着一整个世界，在飘渺的云雾中，悲伤的灵魂像是离开了身体，看着梁上柱慢慢地进入了梦乡<br>梁柱同时也可以理解为梁祝，表达了诗人对美好生活的向往</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
